{"id": "1525943572111691796", "channel_id": "1525943572111691796", "author_id": "939547142090018816", "author_name": "snorlax01", "content": "With the release of more Awakeners, the current Banner Schedule with Triple Rerun would feel much slower. And I honestly always found it pretty odd, knowing that there are 4 Realms but only 3 at a time were rerun once a Month. By rerunning an Awakener from each Realm, the schedule can be sped up and the player retention could conversely be kept; as it can honestly feel pretty boring, playing with the same Awakeners all the time. It would also feel pretty nice knowing that your favourite Realm would always have a Character reran once a Month, and if you're lucky maybe its also one that you really want or need.\n\nIdea pitched by <@149519085275709440>", "timestamp": "2026-07-12T19:14:58.252000+00:00", "thread_id": "1525943572111691796", "edited_timestamp": "2026-07-12T19:15:51.852000+00:00", "mentions": ["149519085275709440"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 15}, {"emoji": "Celeste_agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 8}, {"emoji": "Corpo_advance", "emoji_id": "1459080545882341376", "count": 5}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "Pandia_love", "emoji_id": "1459078512303411261", "count": 3}]}
